item.title: Pro-Palestinian protests continue at colleges across the US
item.description: Pro-Palestinian protests continue at major US universities, and several schools have called police to remove demonstrators. Follow for live updates.

item.title: Yemen's Houthi rebels claim downing US Reaper drone, release footage showing wreckage of aircraft
item.description: They aired footage of parts that corresponded to known pieces of the aircraft.

item.title: April 27, 2024 - Campus protest updates
item.description: Pro-Palestinian protests continue at major US universities, where several schools have called police on protesters, leading to the arrests of hundreds across the country. Follow for live updates.

item.title: Climber dead, another seriously injured after 1,000-foot fall off Alaska mountain
item.description: A 52-year-old woman died and her climbing partner was seriously injured after they fell some 1,000 feet off of a mountain in Denali National Park, officials said.
